'''Necr'ygor Omic wine''' was an expensive [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage from the [[Necr'ygor system/Legends|Necr'ygor system]]. The [[LoBue Cantina]] in the [[Abregado system/Legends|Abregado system]] was known to serve it, and it was a favorite of [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian's]], whose preference was a '49 vintage.

